## Description {#details}

A thin wrapper to store two values that we matched as div-rem pair.

We want this extra indirection to avoid dealing with RAUW&#39;ing the map keys.

Definition at line 76 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/scalar/divrempairs-cpp">DivRemPairs.cpp</a>.
